Name: Read Alignment BEnchMArk
Author: Manuel Holtgrewe <manuel.holtgrewe@fu-berlin.de>
Maintainer: Manuel Holtgrewe <manuel.holtgrewe@fu-berlin.de>
License: GPL v3
Copyright: 2010-2013, FU Berlin
Status: mature
Homepage: http://seqan.de/projects/rabema.html
Description: RABEMA is a benchmark for read mappers.
 Given a reference sequence and a set of reads, RABEMA allows the generation
 of a gold standard based on a well-defined mathematical formulation of the
 read mapping problem.
 .
 See the project website and README file for more information.
 .
 A forthcoming publication will describe the method in detail.
